snippet: The results of a second set of tests to determine what caused the death of the champion Norwegian swimmer Alexander Dale Oen are not expected until late June at the earliest, officials said.
abstract: Swimming officials do not expect results of second set of tests to determine what caused the death of Norwegian swimmer Alexander Dale Oen until late June at the earliest.
lead_paragraph: The results of a second set of tests to determine what caused the death of the champion Norwegian swimmer Alexander Dale Oen are not expected until late June at the earliest, officials said.
